  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Radio Frequency (RF) Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Our client is seeking an RF / Microwave Engineer to support the design, testing, and integration of RF and microwave subsystems for mission-critical systems. This role involves hands-on engineering work across laboratory, field, and customer environments, contributing to system qualification and delivery.</p><h3>Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Design, analyse, and test RF/Microwave components and subsystems</li><li>Source and evaluate COTS components in collaboration with vendors and subcontractors</li><li>Perform RF performance testing, measurement, and troubleshooting in lab and field environments</li><li>Develop test plans, procedures, and reports for RF/Microwave validation</li><li>Prepare technical documentation, design specifications, and drawings</li><li>Support system installation, integration, testing, and qualification activities</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Electrical & Electronics / RF / Microwave Engineering or equivalent</li><li>Minimum 2 years of relevant RF/Microwave experience</li><li>Strong knowledge of RF/Microwave circuits and components (e.g. power amplifiers, waveguides, antennas, circulators)</li><li>Experience with RF simulation tools (CST, ANSYS HFSS, Keysight ADS) is an advantage</li><li>Hands-on experience with RF test equipment (Spectrum Analyzer, VNA, Power Meter, Oscilloscope)</li><li>Strong analytical, troubleshooting, and problem-solving skills</li><li>Hands-on, team-oriented, and willing to work at customer sites (including outdoor environments)</li><li>Willing to be attached to customer premises for at least 24 months</li><li>Singaporeans Only</li></ul><h3>To Apply</h3><p>To apply<strong> </strong>or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p>",
